## 5. Bulk question generation — all categories

Use this workflow whenever expanding or creating questions for **any** category file (not only astronomy).

### Step-by-step workflow

1. **Read the target file** and, if available, `git show HEAD:<file>.json` — preserve existing high-quality questions; do not overwrite good items with templates.
2. **Check global uniqueness** — load stems from all other `*.json` files; never duplicate a `question` string repo-wide.
3. **Research real facts first** — Malayalam Wikipedia / Sarvavijnanakosam / official sources (see §6). Build a fact list: persons, dates, places, measurements, schemes, works — each row must have a **distinct** correct answer.
4. **Write questions from facts** — one or two question angles per fact is fine (e.g. year ↔ event); do **not** loop `for n in range(500)` with fake numbered names to hit a count target.
5. **Reject filler at write time** — apply universal banned patterns (below) in code (`is_filler()` / `add_q()` guards) or manually before save.
6. **Malayalamize** — full Malayalam stems and options; run `python3 apply_malayalam_rules.py <file>.json`.
7. **Validate** — grep for filler patterns; check duplicate stems; spot-read 20 random questions for natural Malayalam and factual sense.
8. **Fail loudly** — if the target count is not reached with real facts, **stop and add more fact data**; never pad with numbered templates (astronomy: `refill_astronomy_unique.py` exits with error instead of padding).

### Universal banned filler patterns (all Malayalam `*.json`)

Reject any question matching these — they indicate bulk template padding, not PSC-quality items:

| Pattern | Example | Why banned |
|---------|---------|------------|
| Numbered fake entity | `പ്രദേശം-42`, `വസ്തുത-17`, `വസ്തു-9` | Not a real place/fact |
| Serial suffix + same answer | `… ജൂൺ-6` … `ജൂൺ-50` → always `ക്ഷുദ്രഗ്രഹം` | Same knowledge repeated |
| Fake catalog numbers | `ഗാലക്സി NGC-1001`, `എക്സ്പ്ലോറർ-184` (no real mission fact) | Interchangeable filler |
| Definition wrapper | `സാമ്പത്തികമായി X … സൂചിപ്പിക്കുന്ന പ്രവർത്തി` | Dictionary gloss, not exam item |
| Recycled distractor tail | `… നടത്തുന്ന സേവനം` on unrelated options | Obvious bulk generation |
| English-only / mixed stem | `RSP in Kerala allied mainly with?` | Violates §1–2 |
| Reverse-meta question | `'X' ഏത് ചോദ്യത്തin's ഉത്തരമാണ്?` | Answer-as-stem; options are other questions |
| Malayalam in `english_language.json` | `ഇംഗ്ലീഷ് വ്യാകരണത്തിൽ Verb …` | English-only file |
| Same template ≥5× same answer | Any stem with only `N` changed | Not conceptually unique |

Real numbered items with **distinct facts** are fine: `ചന്ദ്രയാൻ-3 വിക്ഷേപിച്ച വർഷം`, `GSAT-14`, `അപ്പോളോ 11`, `PSLV-C25` — each must have its own verifiable answer.

